## ğŸš€ Features

* âš¡ **Instant window renaming**
* ğŸ” **Cycle between Dofus windows** (forward/backward)
* ğŸ–¥ï¸ **Toggle workspaces** with a single key
* ğŸ“ **Profiles management** â€” save/load different window setups
* ğŸ§  **Script generator** â€” automatically creates shell scripts for each action
* ğŸª¶ **Fast and minimal PyQt6 GUI** for setup and configuration
* ğŸ¯ Designed for **power users** â€” full keyboard or macro binding support

